\SE[2]This is Laura's place... It seems like it. \SE[0]You can
become stronger here. Are you happy?

\SE[19]I wonder if even I can become strong...? \SE[51]What
should I do if I can't clear the trial...?

\SE\SE[0]Don't worry. You can do it. \.Believe in the efforts
you've made so far... Let's go as usual. \!\SE[0]And if by any
chance...\........

\SE\SE[1] If someone were to deny my Laura... \SE[0] Whether they
are a spirit or not, I will make them obey, no matter what it
takes. \SE[1] So, there is absolutely nothing that you should be
worried about.
\SE[75] (This is the biggest source of anxiety, isn't it?)

\SE\SE[14]Thank you...! But, it's okay! \SE[14]I want to earn the
recognition of the spirits with my own power...!

\SE[54]Laura...! You've become so splendid...! \SE[23]I... I'm
embarrassed about myself...!

\SE[4]Today's Flirting Quota is probably enough, don't you think?
\SE[3]Shall we go soon? The spirits might be getting tired of
waiting... or so I think.

The 'Trial of the Wind' has been added to the teleportation
crystal!

\SE[57]There are many rare creatures here.... \!\SE[58]If I were
to sell their fur, perhaps...?
